Package: cpf
Type: Package
Title: Cohesion Policy Funds 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Anna Olena Zhabyak
Maintainer: Anna Olena Zhabyak <annaolena.zhab@unimi.it>
Description: This package contains functions to plot a dataframe containing the total aamount of funds by country for the EU Cohesion policy 2014/2020. It also contains a shiny app to interact with a basic interface with all the Member states and the total funds by country.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: ggplot2, devtools, utils, rlang, shiny, shinythemes
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
